      <title>财务困境加剧，碧桂园销售额进一步下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/country-garden-extends-sales-slump-as-financial-woes-pile-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[碧桂园控股有限公司(Country Garden Holdings Co.)上个月的房屋销售量较上年同期大幅下滑，这给这家已经面临清盘申请并错过了发布年度业绩的最后期限的中国开发商带来了更大的麻烦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/country-garden-extends-sales-slump-as-financial-woes-pile-up</guid>
